fewShots.question: how many employees are good on supervision?
fewShots.query:
select [rows].[service_month] as [service_month],
    [rows].[achieved] as [achieved],
    count(1) as [count]
from 
(
    select [service_month],
        [achieved]
    from [credible_lakehouse].[silver].[combined_supervision_totals] as [$Table]
) as [rows]
group by [service_month],
    [achieved]
